Name: bianc8

Name: leal.eth
Description: Hello, I’m Leal.eth! As the co-founder of Talent, I’m all about redefining how we connect and collaborate in the professional world. Your support will enable me to continue pushing forward innovative solutions that open up new opportunities for creators and developers alike. Join me on this journey!

Name: limone.eth
Description: Hi there! I’m Limone.eth, your friendly neighborhood lemon! I’m on a mission to build on-chain products and vibrant communities with Builders Garden. I love creating projects like Urbe-Eth and Ethrome, where creativity and collaboration come to life. By supporting me, you’re helping to nurture decentralized spaces where everyone can thrive and grow. Let’s spread some zest in the Web3 world together!
